'''《共產中國與自由世界的未來》'''（{{lang-en|Communist China and the Free World's Future}}）是[[美國|美國]][[美国国务卿|國務卿]][[邁克·蓬佩奧|邁克·蓬佩奧]]於2020年7月23日在[[尼克松总统图书馆暨博物馆|尼克松总统图书馆暨博物馆]]進行的演講。在當中，他呼籲[[自由世界|自由世界]]團結起來和[[中國人|中國人]]一起改變[[中國共產黨|中國共產黨]]<ref name="Pompeo">{{cite web |last = Pompeo |first = Michael R. |title = Communist China and the Free World's Future |url = https://www.state.gov/communist-china-and-the-free-worlds-future/ |date=2020-07-23 |access-date=2020-07-28 |website = state.gov |publisher = [[United_States_Department_of_State|United States Department of State]] |archive-date = 2020-07-29 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200729101237/https://www.state.gov/communist-china-and-the-free-worlds-future/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Choi">{{cite web |last = Choi |first = Matthew |date = 2020-07-23 |title = Pompeo: U.S. engagement with China has failed |url = https://www.politico.com/news/2020/07/23/pompeo-china-speech-nixon-380251 |dead-url=no |access-date=2020-07-29|website=Politico |archive-date=2020-07-28|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200728182641/https://www.politico.com/news/2020/07/23/pompeo-china-speech-nixon-380251 }}</ref>。在演講中，蓬佩奧稱讚[[中國人|中國人]]是個充滿活力、熱愛[[自由|自由]]的[[中华民族|民族]]，與[[中國共產黨|中國共產黨]]完全不同，他還批評「[[習近平|習近平]]總書記是一位业已[[破產|破產]]的[[極權主義|極權主義]][[意識形態|意識形態]]的真正信仰者」（{{lang-en|General Secretary Xi Jinping is a true believer in a bankrupt totalitarian ideology}}）<ref>{{cite web |title = 教育与文化  使馆及领馆    新闻及活动 共产主义中国和自由世界的未来 |url = https://china.usembassy-china.org.cn/zh/communist-china-and-the-free-worlds-future-zh/ |publisher = 美国驻华大使馆和领事馆 |access-date=2020-08-08 |archive-date=2020-07-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200726183116/https://china.usembassy-china.org.cn/zh/communist-china-and-the-free-worlds-future-zh/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[BBC|BBC]]將蓬佩奧的此次演講視為開啟[[第二次冷戰|第二次冷戰]]的新[[铁幕|铁幕]]演讲<ref>{{cite news |title = 蓬佩奥发表“新铁幕演讲” 呼吁世界和中国人“改变中国共产党” |url = https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-53519761 |publisher=BBC |access-date=2020-08-14 |archive-date=2020-08-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200807174538/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-53519761 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==背景==
《共產中國與自由世界的未來》發表時，最早在[[中華人民共和國|中華人民共和國]][[湖北省|湖北省]][[武漢市|武漢市]]爆發的[[2019冠狀病毒病|2019冠狀病毒病]]已蔓延至全球各國，[[中華人民共和國|中華人民共和國]][[全國人大常委會|全國人大常委會]]趁全球各國飽受[[2019冠狀病毒病疫情|2019冠狀病毒病疫情]]之苦的時候，通過[[港版國安法|港版國安法]]鎮壓[[香港|香港]][[反送中運動|反送中運動]]，[[2018－2020年中美贸易战|中美貿易戰]]第一階段協議亦於此時執行。之前，国家安全顾问[[罗伯特·C·奥布莱恩|罗伯特·C·奥布莱恩]]、联邦调查局局长[[克里斯托弗·A·雷|克里斯托弗·A·雷]]及司法部长[[威廉·巴尔|威廉·巴尔]]等川普政府官員先后分别在亚利桑那州、哈德逊研究所和福特总统博物馆就美中关系发表了系列公开讲话， 介绍了美中在意识形态、情报及经济领域里的对抗。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_J-Fqe9Xdi4&t=629s |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-01-17 |archive-date=2021-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122223359/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_J-Fqe9Xdi4&t=629s }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=89SMHyn7iCE |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-01-17 |archive-date=2022-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220215142739/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=89SMHyn7iCE }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5jEqZVZKGaM |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-01-17 |archive-date=2020-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201220172228/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5jEqZVZKGaM }}</ref>

== 内容 ==
[[File:Secretary_Pompeo_Delivers_a_Speech_at_the_Richard_Nixon_Presidential_Library_(50147332516).jpg|thumb]]
蓬佩奥国务卿在尼克松总统图书馆的讲话则全面阐述了川普政府对美中关系前途的看法，“详述中国的威胁对我们的经济、自由乃至全球自由民主国家的未来所产生的意义”<ref name="Pompeo" />。

演讲开头先抛出对中美建交50年的疑问。他表示，如果世界仍想保持自由的话，“跟中国盲目交往的老旧范式是走不通的”<ref name="Pompeo" />。他提到中国对“[[武漢病毒|武漢病毒]]”、[[香港|香港]][[反送中運動|反送中運動]]、[[新疆集中營|新疆集中營]]、贸易霸凌及军队愈发“险恶”等问题的处理及回应<ref name="Pompeo" /><ref name="Choi" />。然而蓬佩奥的演讲将[[中国人|中国人]]和[[中国共产党|中国共产党]]进行区分，表示“我们必须同时与中国人民进行交往，给予他们权利，他们是一群充满活力、热爱自由的人，跟中国共产党完全不同”<ref>{{Cite news|last=Delaney|first=Robert|date=2020-07-24|title=Pompeo urges China's citizens to help change Beijing's 'behaviour'|url=https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3094467/us-secretary-state-urges-chinas-citizens-help-change-behaviour|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-07-29|work=South China Morning Post|archive-date=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728092105/https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3094467/us-secretary-state-urges-chinas-citizens-help-change-behaviour}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last=Raj|first=Yashwant|date=2020-07-24|title=US abandons China appeasement policy, outsources hostilities|url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/world-news/us-abandons-china-appeasement-policy-outsources-hostilities/story-1bTN5CXWZb6NJZ64dBaSSL.html|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-07-29|work=Hindustan Times|archive-date=2020-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200730035134/https://www.hindustantimes.com/world-news/us-abandons-china-appeasement-policy-outsources-hostilities/story-1bTN5CXWZb6NJZ64dBaSSL.html}}</ref>。演讲表示，“最大的谎言莫过于中国共产党为受监视、压迫，害怕发声的14亿人代言”，而真相是“中国共产党害怕中国人的诚实观点，胜过外国敌人<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|last=Greber|first=Jacob|date=2020-07-23|title=Pompeo unleashes on China, urges West to 'change' the Communist Party|url=https://www.afr.com/world/north-america/pompeo-unleashes-on-china-urges-west-to-change-the-communist-party-20200724-p55ezn|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200802054301/https://www.afr.com/world/north-america/pompeo-unleashes-on-china-urges-west-to-change-the-communist-party-20200724-p55ezn|archive-date=2020-08-02|access-date=2020-07-30|website=Australian Financial Review|language=en}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite news|last1=O’Keeffe|first1=Kate|last2=Mauldin|first2=William|date=2020-07-24|title=Mike Pompeo Urges Chinese People to Change Communist Party|language=en-US|work=Wall Street Journal|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/secretary-of-state-pompeo-to-urge-chinese-people-to-change-the-communist-party-11595517729|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-07-30|issn=0099-9660|archive-date=2020-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200730140110/https://www.wsj.com/articles/secretary-of-state-pompeo-to-urge-chinese-people-to-change-the-communist-party-11595517729}}</ref>”。他表示[[中国共产党中央委员会总书记|中国共产党中央委员会总书记]][[习近平|习近平]]是“濒临破产的极权主义意识形态的真正信徒”<ref>{{Cite web|last=Churchill|first=Owen|title=US officials now call Xi Jinping 'general secretary' instead of China's 'president' – but why?|url=https://www.scmp.com/news/world/united-states-canada/article/3094669/us-officials-switch-calling-chinas-xi-jinping|date=2020-07-25|access-date=2020-07-25|website=South China Morning Post|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200724220251/https://www.scmp.com/news/world/united-states-canada/article/3094669/us-officials-switch-calling-chinas-xi-jinping|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Re|first=Gregg|title=Pompeo announces end of 'blind engagement' with communist China: 'Distrust but verify'|url=https://www.foxnews.com/politics/pompeo-announces-end-blind-engagement-communist-china|date=2020-07-23|access-date=2020-07-23|website=Fox News|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200723230318/https://www.foxnews.com/politics/pompeo-announces-end-blind-engagement-communist-china|dead-url=no}}</ref>。蓬佩奥呼吁自由世界联手帮助中国改革<ref name="Pompeo" />。

=== 演讲指涉 ===
==== 自由世界 ====
在讲话中，蓬佩奥在提到自由世界与中共等共产主义政权的斗争时，多次使用“[[自由世界|自由世界]]”一词。这其中包括针对中國追求“小国服从于大国的屈从式国际制度，而不是小国共享平等权利、依规则形成的国际制度”的人士发起的斗争，以及对不关心[[自然权利|自然权利]]或{{le|开放市场|open market}}的中国共产党发起的斗争<ref name="Wright">{{Cite web|last=Wright|first=Thomas|date=2020-07-27|title=Pompeo's surreal speech on China|url=https://www.brookings.edu/blog/order-from-chaos/2020/07/27/pompeos-surreal-speech-on-china/|access-date=2020-07-29|website=Brookings|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803145900/https://www.brookings.edu/blog/order-from-chaos/2020/07/27/pompeos-surreal-speech-on-china/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。蓬佩奥指出，自由世界的公平屬性，为中国培育了健康的经济，但中国共产党却反过来剥削自由世界<ref>{{Cite web|last=Hansler|first=Jennifer|date=2020-07-24|title=Pompeo blasts Beijing as deadline nears for China to shutter Houston consulate|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/07/23/politics/pompeo-china-nixon-library-speech/index.html|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-07-29|website=CNN|archive-date=2020-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729085154/https://www.cnn.com/2020/07/23/politics/pompeo-china-nixon-library-speech/index.html}}</ref>。

==== 理查德·尼克松 ====
演讲提到了[[理查德·尼克松|理查德·尼克松]]与中国接触的政策。讲话指，尼克松在他的一篇讲中美关系的文章中表示，“只有中国改革，世界才会安全”，而美国的目标“应该是促成变革”<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-07-24|title=Pompeo Echoes Nixon's Words: 'World Cannot Be Safe Until China Changes'|url=http://www.eurasiareview.com/24072020-pompeo-echoes-nixons-words-world-cannot-be-safe-until-china-changes/|access-date=2020-07-29|website=Eurasia Review|archive-date=2020-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902163433/https://www.eurasiareview.com/24072020-pompeo-echoes-nixons-words-world-cannot-be-safe-until-china-changes/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite magazine|last=Nixon|first=Richard M.|author-link=Richard Nixon|date=October 1967|title=Asia After Viet Nam|magazine=Foreign Affairs|volume=46|number=1|url=https://www.foreignaffairs.com/articles/asia/1967-10-01/asia-after-viet-nam|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-07-29|archive-date=2020-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200730143321/https://www.foreignaffairs.com/articles/asia/1967-10-01/asia-after-viet-nam}}</ref>。蓬佩奥认为，尼克松对中共的形容已经变成“[[弗兰肯斯坦的怪物|弗兰肯斯坦的怪物]]”<ref>{{Cite news|last1=Brunnstrom|first1=David|last2=Psaledakis|first2=Daphne|date=2020-07-24|title=Pompeo urges more assertive approach to 'Frankenstein' China|agency=Reuters|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-china-pompeo/pompeo-urges-more-assertive-approach-to-frankenstein-china-idUSKCN24O310|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-07-29|archive-date=2020-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729050708/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-china-pompeo/pompeo-urges-more-assertive-approach-to-frankenstein-china-idUSKCN24O310}}</ref>。

==== 苏联 ====
演講中提到，中共正重蹈[[苏联|苏联]]过去犯下的错误。但又指中共与苏联有所不同，中共追求中国在全球形势能实现规模更大的一体化<ref name="Pompeo" />。蓬佩奥也提到了[[罗纳德·里根|罗纳德·里根]]讲苏联问题时用过的“[[信任，但要核实|信任，但要核实]]”一词，认为放在中共身上应变成“不信任，而且要核实”<ref name="Raj 2020-07-25">{{Cite news|last=Raj|first=Yashwant|date=2020-07-25|title=Distrust and verify: US ups ante against China|url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/distrust-and-verify-us-ups-ante-against-china/story-9OHZT9gGipDs2W14RIf1zJ.html|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-07-29|work=Hindustan Times|archive-date=2020-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200730033324/https://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/distrust-and-verify-us-ups-ante-against-china/story-9OHZT9gGipDs2W14RIf1zJ.html}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last1=Fang|first1=Alex|last2=Moriyasu|first2=Ken|date=2020-07-24|title=Distrust and verify: Pompeo refits Cold War slogan for China|url=https://asia.nikkei.com/Politics/International-relations/Distrust-and-verify-Pompeo-refits-Cold-War-slogan-for-China|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-07-29|website=Nikkei Asian Review|archive-date=2020-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729045454/https://asia.nikkei.com/Politics/International-relations/Distrust-and-verify-Pompeo-refits-Cold-War-slogan-for-China}}</ref>。

==== 异见者 ====
[[File:Secretary_Pompeo_Meets_With_Chinese_Dissidents_and_Members_of_the_Diaspora_(50147012718).jpg|thumb]]委员[[努里·特克尔|努里·特克尔]]（左四）、中国持不同政见人士[[魏京生|魏京生]]（右四）和[[王丹|王丹]]（右三），以及侨民代表。]]
蓬佩奥在演讲中提到[[罗冠聪|罗冠聪]]、[[魏京生|魏京生]]和[[王丹|王丹]]。魏京生和王丹出席了此次活动，蓬佩奥让他们向观众问好。蓬佩奥称魏京生“中国民主运动之父”、称[[六四事件|六四事件]]幸存者王丹为“从未停止为中国人民争取自由的关键学生”。蓬佩奥认为，“中国异见者曾警告我们所面对政权的本质”，而这些话常常被前任的美国领导者忽略，美国与异见者的接触将会逐渐增加<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-07-24|others=PTI|title=US seeks new 'alliance of democracies' to take on authoritarian Chinese regime: Pompeo - The Economic Times|url=https://m.economictimes.com/news/defence/us-seeks-new-alliance-of-democracies-to-take-on-authoritarian-chinese-regime-pompeo/amp_articleshow/77141893.cms|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902163433/https://m.economictimes.com/news/defence/us-seeks-new-alliance-of-democracies-to-take-on-authoritarian-chinese-regime-pompeo/amp_articleshow/77141893.cms|archive-date=2020-09-02|access-date=2020-07-30|website=Economic Times (Mobile)}}</ref><ref name=":0" />。

==== 好莱坞 ====
蓬佩奥认为[[好莱坞|好莱坞]]是“美国创意自由的中心”，也是“自认社会正义仲裁者”的云集之地。但眼下好莱坞的自由审查极为严重，即便是最轻微的对中国不利指涉都会被抹去<ref name="Hewitt">{{Cite news|last=Hewitt|first=Hugh|date=2020-07-25|title=Opinion {{!}} Pompeo's speech opens a bold new chapter in U.S.-China relations|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/2020/07/24/pompeos-speech-opens-bold-new-chapter-us-china-relations/|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-07-29|work=The Washington Post|archive-date=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728152904/https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/2020/07/24/pompeos-speech-opens-bold-new-chapter-us-china-relations/}}</ref>。

